Package com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultFormattingStrategy
    This implements an iFormattingStrategy to format documents.
    MQSCAutoIndentStrategy
    This performs indentation on lines in the MQSC Document as relevant based on their content.
    MQSCCompletionProcessor
    This reacts to requests for code completion and produces the relevant suggestions based on where in the MQSC command the request came from.
    MQSCCompletionProcessor.Validator  
    MQSCContentOutlineLabelProvider
    This assigns a default image to each item in the outline view.
    MQSCContentOutlinePage
    This builds the contents of the Outline view.
    MQSCContentOutlinePage.Segment  
    MQSCDamagerRepairer
    This extends the DefaultDamagerRepairer to register a scanner and return the correct partition.
    MQSCDoubleClickSelector
    This implements an ITextDoubleClickStrategy to select and match brackets or words or etc.
    MQSCFormattingStrategy
    This extends the DefaultFormattingStrategy to format MQSC commands to specific line widths.
